	<body>
		<h1>Below are special characters and their proper code.</h1>
			Quotation marks &quot; uses the &amp;quot; code.
			<br>
			Apostrophes &#39; use the &amp;#39; code.
			<br>
			Empty or Blank spaces &nbsp;&nbsp; use the &amp;nbsp; code.
			<br>
			Ampersands &amp; use the “&amp;amp; code.
			<br>
			Copyright symbol &copy; uses the &amp;copy;” code.
		<p>These are just a few special character codes. More can be found at https://www.w3schools.com/html/html_symbols.asp </p>

	</body>
</html>
